  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the present study is to assess the efficacy of methylprednisolone as an
      adjuvant therapy in patients with severe community-acquired pneumonia (CAP) (PSI 4-5).

      The hypothesis of the study is that methylprednisolone can decrease the mortality of severe
      CAP without any significant side effects,with reduction of the time to clinical stability and
      failure rate of treatment.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
